title: Matt Pryor from The Get Up Kids/New Amsterdams
itunes:title: Matt Pryor from The Get Up Kids/New Amsterdams
description:
I met up with Matt Pryor one evening at a show he performed here in Southern California so please forgive the background noise that you hear. Matt and I discuss balancing road life and family life, age gaps and selling out. It was a very insightful chat that I am happy to bring you.
